text: Nadvoitsy () is the name of several inhabited localities in Segezhsky District of the Republic of Karelia, Russia: *Nadvoitsy, an urban locality (an urban- type settlement) *Nadvoitsy (rural locality), a rural locality (a village) ==See also== *Pristan Nadvoitsy, a rural locality (a station) in Segezhsky District of the Republic of Karelia
title: Nadvoitsy (inhabited locality)
